Description: An amazing musician has been diagnosed with MS, and like many musicians, he does not have health insurance. One of the ways we are supporting this musicians is by auctioning off this guitar.Help us help him with his treatment and living expenses by purchasing this Charvel Desolation DST-3 FR White Star Electric Guitar .We appreciate your support and generosity. More photos upon request. The Desolation Star DST-3 FR 1H hails the return of Charvel’s classic Star body profile, with features including a bolt-on maple neck with angled heel, 12”-radius rosewood fingerboard with 24 jumbo frets and dot inlays, single humbucking pickup with black bezel, single domed metal volume control knob, Floyd Rose® locking tremolo, sealed die-cast tuners and black nickel hardware. With a variety of features and finishes, the Desolation Star DST delivers the devastating tone, killer looks and high-performance playability that separate the Desolation series from others.
